Intro Vi, Vim, Neovim&hellip;
The Vi based text editors are known for their complexity, nuance, and speed, for those who learn it.
I happen to love using Neovim as my primary text editor, and find it super beneficial to writing and editing text files. I do try to use text files more often than the average person, using Markdown where ever possible over Word, or other word processors, for example.
